  <p>And if you're thinking that 200 times the bet isn't that impressive, let us tell you that winning that much is like finding a pot of gold at the end of the rainbow. But be warned, just like the treasure at the end of the rainbow, the jackpot might be elusive. Just don't give up at the first sign of trouble, because remember, patience is a virtue, and just like in life, the biggest rewards often require the most patience.</p>"
